    "text": "I didn't know that, what do you mean?"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "Buddy, the bank thing"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 1,
    "text": "What bank?"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "It was super viral, some guys robbed a bank leaving unsubtle clues trying to blame Sentinel and such, I'm not sure what they were trying to achieve with that."
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "The point is that in a matter of a few days, all the members of the robbery were handed over to the police by real members of Sentinel. The same week of being incarcerated, they all died on the same day and at the same time"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 1,
    "text": "Cyber-curse?"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "Haha well at the beginning it sounded like this, each one was killed by other prisoners, but clearly Sentinel wanted to send a message, as if they were everywhere. Not only that, but later it has been known that direct relatives with the robbers have suffered great misfortunes, such as suspicious deaths, drug addiction, etc. But well, that could be a coincidence, in any case, it seems that it worked, no one else has thought of pretending to be them. "
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 1,
    "text": "Uff they are not what I thought..."
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "I was surprised that you were so surprised xD everyone knows that it is not the first time they have killed."
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 1,
    "text": "But hacking the military drones and killing all the soldiers at the base I don't think is the solution."
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "Don't try to make much sense of what they do."
  }
]

