content.CONV_BK_MISSION_3:
[
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "You won't believe what happened to me"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 1,
    "text": "What's wrong?"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "Do you remember I told you that I was going to go hiking this weekend with the dog in the mountains?"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "Well, walking near a river, Seymour started digging under a tree quite insistently..."
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 1,
    "text": "Uuh have you found a body?"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "Hahaha no! Much better!"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 1,
    "text": "..."
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "A backpack full of money! Ha!"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 1,
    "text": "It's certainly better than a corpse..."
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 1,
    "text": "Come on, seriously, did you find something or are you kidding me?"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 1,
    "text": "Don't waste my time, I have a lot of things to do today"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "I swear it's true."
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "I've counted it several times, exactly 5 million..."
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "I just sent you a photo :)"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "I have thrown the backpack and am putting the money in a more secure box."
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 1,
    "text": "But... that money have an owner, someone will have hidden it there"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "And how are they going to know who it was?"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "There was no one when I picked it up."
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 1,
    "text": "OMG I think you're getting into something dangerous."
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 1,
    "text": "Do you think that whoever hid it there will not have the means to get to the money in some way?"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 1,
    "text": "I would take it to the police, tell them that you have found it by chance and forget about it"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 0,
    "text": "How exaggerated you are, but I appreciate the advice, I'll think about it :)"
  },
  {
    "idNpc": 1,
    "text": "I wouldn't take long to think about it if it were you."
  },
